example.programlisting:
...
# Only INVITE/BYE webhooks, batched in groups of 10
modparam("rust_http_webhook", "method_filter", "INVITE,BYE")
modparam("rust_http_webhook", "batch_size", 10)
modparam("rust_http_webhook", "batch_timeout_ms", 200)

route {
    webhook("{\"method\":\"$rm\",\"from\":\"$fu\",\"ruri\":\"$ru\",\"ts\":\"$Ts\"}");
}
...

section.para:
Number of webhook calls that were skipped because the &sip;
request method did not match the
method_filter configuration.
